==Editor==
[[File:John Betjeman, London, England, GB, IMG 4991 edit.jpg|thumb|upright|Betjeman's statue at [[St Pancras railway station]]]]

Betjeman undertook the role of editor for several magazines and journals, including the undergraduate magazines of ''Oxford Outlook'' and ''[[Cherwell (newspaper)|Cherwell]]''; the following consists of the books he edited.{{sfn|Peterson|2006|p=305}}

